{Sally in the kitchen.}
You need a{skipping rope}to play this game.We jump in and then sing this {song.} Sally in the kitchen doing a bit of stitching.In comes a bogey man and knocks Sally out. If you catch the rope on your leg you are out.We take it in turns to have a go.
{Another skipping song.}
Ala Bala Boosha,king of the Koosha, bought his wife a pair of shoes.When the shoes began to wear Ala Bala Boosha began to swear and these are the words he said,"Lady, Lady, turn around.Lady, Lady, touch the ground. Lady, Lady, show your shoe.Lady,lady out with you. O U T spells out."
